high_descs: Take one step then turn to the right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and pick up the coffee cup that is on the shelf.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the coffee cup inside, then close the door and turn the microwave for three seconds, then take the coffee cup out of the microwave.
Turn to the left and take one step, then turn to the left and take two steps, then turn to the right and walk across the room.
Put the coffee cup on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the coffee cup in the microwave.

high_descs: Take two steps forward, turn right and take four steps and stop in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door and pick up the coffee mug from the second shelf then shut the fridge door.
Turn right for two steps, turn right again and take six steps, turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the mug on the plate in the microwave, turn on the microwave for a few second, open the door, take out the mug and shut the door again.
Turn left and take three steps, take another left for six steps, turn right and walk to the counter and stand in front of the coffee machine.
Set the coffee cup on the design on the silver metal of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Take a warmed coffee cup and set it on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black fridge.
Open the fridge, pick up the white mug from the middle shelf and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the left.
Put the mug inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the coffee maker on the counter to the right.
Put the heated mug on the platform of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug on a coffee maker.
